overview:
McCartney Kay Auto Cosmetics, LLC is a one-stop-shop for the fashionable woman driver looking for ways to add that personal touch of flare, femininity and personality to her vehicle! You’ll find everything from stylish, decorative accessories to useful tools for organization and safety that no woman should be without – because every woman should be able to personalize her vehicle just as much as men do!

If you are looking for a high quality dash cam in car camera with DVR and audio, look no further! The TD Dash Cam is affordable and easy to use.

The affordable TD dashboard camera is easy to install. Simply clip the dash cam in-car camera onto your visor and plug the power cord into the cigarette lighter. Great for capturing video of the driver’s view or the interior of the vehicle. Dash cam videos are recorded on a micro SD card in AVI file format, for later playback on your PC, laptop or TV using the AV cable, or USB 2.0 Cable. Records up to 48 hours of continuous video/audio on a 32 GB micro SD card. (TD Dash Cam includes a FREE 8 GB SD Card) The TD Dash Cam with built-in DVR, crystal clear audio & high-resolution 720x480 pixel screen and 30 frames per second recording. With the new TD Dash Cam you can easily record your driver’s view OR interior view in real time with audio. Taxi, limousine, truck drivers, bus drivers & every day drivers can record everything that happens in the vehicle while driving with our dash cam in-car camera system. Police use it as evidence and to protect themselves from wrongful prosecution, shouldn’t you? Tire of hearing “Tell it to the judge”? Now you can show it to the judge with the time and date stamped on the video.

AutoTex Pink Plus windshield wiper blades come in a standard pink color, with a small pink ribbon promoting the cause of breast cancer awareness and research. They are available in metal or frameless. Fits over 98% of vehicles on the road, Natural molded rubber for longer life, Meets or exceeds SAE specifications and Easy installation in as little as five minutes The AutoTex PINK PLUS wiper blade is the optimal wiper replacement for drivers who are both concerned with ensuring safety through improved visibility on the road and making a bold statement.

Dress your car’s headlights to match your own style, fashion and sparkle with the Eyelashes for your car in Black or Pink Eyelashes. Simply attach the Headlight lashes to your car using the 3M automotive tape supplied, the flexible design of the lashes allows them to bend round almost any car headlight.

The Car•go Handbag Hook is distinctively designed to add convenience and style to your car’s interior. The simple snap clip easily swings around to offer several placement options for securing a wide variety of items such as grocery bags, laptop bags, totes with longer straps and much more! A Car•go hook can also keep your belongings up off of the dirty floor mats and away from muddy shoes during carpool, keep your grocery sack and take-out food upright, prevent your rear seat DVD headphone set from being sat or stepped on, your wet umbrella off the floor and on and on … The possibilities are endless! Additional Uses: Grocery Bag Laptop Bag Rear Seat DVD Headphones Kid’s Book Bags Coat / Sweater Briefcase Diaper Bag Gym & Sporting Duffel Backpacks Sporting Equipment Beach Tote Umbrellas (Especially when wet!)
